room_title: Escape room "Champagne Room" by Escape Artist Texas in Houston
review: This was fun. Well done and a great challenge. Worth checking out.

room_title: Escape room "Champagne Room" by Escape Artist Texas in Houston
review: My husband and I had such a fun and unique date night here. Everyone was incredibly friendly and we had a blast! We will absolutely be returning.

room_title: Escape room "Champagne Room" by Escape Artist Texas in Houston
review: This was my first time and also the group of friends that I went with,it was their first time also doing an escape room and the owners and staff were very nice and accommodating to our group . Our group was split into two different theme rooms ,some did the kill room and hubby and I ended up doing the champagne room this was the hardest room but we had so much fun although we weren't successful we look forward to coming back soon ! Highly recommend
